@startuml
title Subscribe & Save Debugging Classroom Activity

class App {
  +getAmazonProductService() : AmazonProductService
  +getIdentityService() : IdentityService
  +getSubscriptionDAO() : SubscriptionDAO
  +getFileStorage() : FileStorage
}

interface IFileStorage {
    get(id) 
    write(data): id
}

abstract class AbstractDao<T> {
   -filestorage: IFileStorage

   create(entity:T): T
   getById(id:String):T   
}


App --> "1" *-- "*" SubscriptionDAO  
AbstractDao <|-- SubscriptionDAO 

note right of SubscriptonDebugUtil::main(String[] args)\nvoid\n{...}\nThe main method creates an instance \nof the subscription service.\nIt then calls subscribe on this object,\npassing in some test data for customerId, ASIN and frequency.
SubcriptioinDebugUtil ..* SubscriptionService 


@enduml
